Angelic entities (which powers and principalities make part of) are bodiless compared to man and bodied compared to Yahweh. Thus also immortal compared to man but mortal compared to Him. No one has really made a different claim I think. Except maybe Varg. He's also a mortal guy.

It's interesting regular viewers often assume the Troy movie quote about how the gods envy men because we are mortal and every day may be our last is something actually from Homer's text, because Greek pagans absolutely knew their gods were also mortal and could be destroyed etc.
Someone here talked about it, but I like the idea that "Yahweh" should be rendered as "Jove" in the European languages and English specifically. As in "by Jove!" Makes it sound very Roman.

Still not over Trump calling the blonde secret service woman "brave and beautiful". Genuinely brilliant choice of words. I think it actually might be my favorite Trump excerpt of all time.

Libtards demand he soys out on how women can do just as good a job as men and training and professionalism is all that matters.

Conservatards want him to start pathetically sobbing "I almost died because of DEI, I could have lost my life because of female quotas, oh, poor me..."

Instead he ignores all that and chooses to praise HER and her PERSONAL qualities. Her strong character. Her physical looks. Nothing of this has anything to do with her job or ability to do it. Brave and beautiful. You just know she blushed when she read it. He's pure magnanimity.
GOBAD stat

I think studying Trump's choice of words here really is the key to understanding his Weltanschauung and why he has always been such a winner no matter what. The total "aristocratic" lack of resentment, the calm assurance in Providence, the smooth, open compliments. It's all here.

Imagine if a female surgeon fucks up and you almost die on the operating table due to her error and after you're resuscitated and wake up, and find out what happened, your first instinct is to say how cute she looks in her scrubs and how smart she is. This is the Trump mindset.
